metadata.name: Daria
metadata.description:
Monochrome series "Daria"

My first shoot was at home without professional lighting - just one lamp from Ikea. Despite all the restrictions, I managed to show all the inner energy of the girl and personify the text written under her breasts - "Hotter than fire."
Captured by Shevchenko Kirill in Tyumen, Sibiria.

*after purchase, the buyer receives access to the remaining 10 photos, in full resolution + 3 bonus photos and adaptation for wallpaper
